int a;
int b;
int c;

int d;

int sqrt;
int n;
int u;

int[2] x;

x[0] := 999;
x[1] := 999;

:*
    Lulululu lul uluuuu
*:

read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);


:* ENDE DER ABC FORMEL

    Ab hier nur noch performance test :-)
*:


read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(b);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);

read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

else {

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

else {
    if( d = 0) {

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;

        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(b);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;

        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(b);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;

        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(b);
read(c);

            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);
read(a);
read(b);
read(c);

        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

d := (b*b) - 4 * a * c;

if( d < 0) { :* a+b+c*d *: }
else {
    if( d = 0) {
       x[0] := ((-b) : (2*a));
    }
    else {

        u := d;
        sqrt := u;
        u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        while(u < sqrt){
            sqrt := u;
            u := (sqrt + (d:sqrt)):2;
        };

        x[0] := (((-b) + sqrt): (2*a));
        x[1] := (((-b) - sqrt): (2*a));
    };
};

write(x[0]);
write(x[1]);

read(b);
read(c);
